Description: <div align='center'>
          <h1>pytest-deprecate</h1>
          <p>Mark tests as testing a deprecated feature with a warning note.</p>
          <p>
            <a href='https://travis-ci.org/NyanKiyoshi/pytest-deprecate/'>
